€In loving memory of Aran Morris
7th January 1951 to 25th December 2012
Softly the leaves of memory fall
Gently we gather and treasure them all
Unseen, unheard, you are always near
So loved, so missed, so very dear."Î
ËROY JAMES PALFREYMAN
1942 - 2003
